贝基·希尔 (Becky Hill) 回应有关她将代表英国参加 2025 年欧洲歌唱大赛的“胡言乱语”报道https://www.nme.com/news/music/becky-hill-responds-to-bollocks-reports-shell-be-representing-uk-at-eurovision-2025-3807651?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=becky-希尔对 2025 年欧洲电视网代表英国的胡言乱语报告作出回应Laura MolloyTue, 29 Oct 2024 20:01:44 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3807651 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Becky-Hill.-CREDIT_-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Becky-Hill.-CREDIT_-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Becky-Hill.-CREDIT_-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Becky-Hill.-CREDIT_-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Becky-Hill.-CREDIT_-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Becky-Hill.-CREDIT_-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Becky-Hill.-CREDIT_-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “以前有人问过我，我的答案没有改变，就是响亮的‘不’”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/becky-hill-responds-to-bollocks-reports-shell-be-representing-uk-at-eurovision-2025-3807651">贝基·希尔 (Becky Hill) 对她将代表英国参加 2025 年欧洲电视网 (Eurovision 2025) 的“胡说八道”报道做出的回应</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Becky-Hill.-CREDIT_-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Becky-Hill.-CREDIT_-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Becky-Hill.-CREDIT_-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Becky-Hill.-CREDIT_-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Becky-Hill.-CREDIT_-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Becky-Hill.-CREDIT_-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Becky-Hill.-CREDIT_-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/becky-hill">贝基·希尔 (Becky Hill)</a>辟谣了有关她将代表英国参加 2025 年欧洲歌唱大赛的传言。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/becky-hill-tells-us-about-new-album-believe-me-now-im-not-the-underdog-anymore-3579114">贝基·希尔 (Becky Hill) 向我们介绍新专辑《现在相信我吗？》(Believe Me Now?)：“我不再是失败者了”</a></strong></li></ul><p>第 69 届欧洲歌唱大赛将在瑞士巴塞尔举行，决赛将于 2025 年 5 月举行。此前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/switzerlands-nemo-wins-eurovision-song-contest-2024-3755482">Nemo 凭借歌曲《The Code》在 2024 年欧洲歌唱大赛上为瑞士夺得冠军</a>。这是该国自 1988 年以来首次获胜，也是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/viewers-react-to-switzerlands-eurovision-win-non-binary-folks-rule-the-world-3755500">欧洲歌唱大赛有史以来第一个非二元获胜者</a>。</p><p>现在，在明年的演出之前，BBC 正在物色下一位代表英国的演员，并已获得<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sam-ryder">萨姆·莱德 (Sam Ryder)</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-ryders-manager-recruited-in-search-for-uks-eurovision-2025-entry-3804089">经纪人大卫·梅 (David May) 的帮助来物色人才</a>。</p><p>目前尚未公布姓名，但最近有人猜测希尔正在竞选，因为欧洲电视网粉丝新闻 Instagram 帐户分享了一篇帖子，称她为“可能的英国代表”。</p><p>然而，这位流行歌手立即驳斥了这一说法，评论道：“哈哈哈谁告诉你这个的？恐怕这是胡说八道，我不会参加欧洲电视网 x”</p><p>然后她继续在她的Instagram故事中分享了这篇文章，并写道：“顺便说一句，这完全是胡说八道，我以前曾被问过，但我的答案没有改变，这是一个响亮的‘不x’” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DBCOujatniK/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5)