have%20defended%20their,over%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza.&amp;text=It%20comes%20ahead%20of%20the,this%20Saturday%20(May%2011).">以色列参加</a>今年的赛事而遭到抗议，但<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/despite-protests-eurovision-2024-breaks-global-viewing-figures-3759333">2024 年欧洲电视网的全球收视率仍打破了纪录</a>。根据<a href="https://www.ebu.ch/news/2024/05/eurovision-song-contest-2024-breaks-new-records-as-hundreds-of-millions-watch-and-listen-on-tv-and-digital-platforms">EBU 的数据</a>，共有 1.63 亿观众收看了包括总决赛在内的三场现场直播赛事。 </p><figure id="attachment_3756380" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3756380" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3756380" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OllyAlexander-Eurovision-2024-statement.jpg" alt="Olly Alexander 在 2024 年欧洲歌唱大赛舞台上现场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OllyAlexander-Eurovision-2024-statement.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OllyAlexander-Eurovision-2024-statement-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OllyAlexander-Eurovision-2024-statement-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OllyAlexander-Eurovision-2024-statement-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OllyAlexander-Eurovision-2024-statement-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OllyAlexander-Eurovision-2024-statement-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3756380" class="wp-caption-text"> Olly Alexander 在 2024 年欧洲歌唱大赛现场表演。图片来源：Martin Sylvest Andersen/Getty</figcaption></figure><p> Israel 的加入引发了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/hundreds-of-queer-artists-urge-olly-alexander-to-boycott-eurovision-2024-over-israels-participation-3610773">LGBT+ 群体对 Olly Alexander 的抵制呼吁，</a>超过 1,000 名瑞典艺术家也<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/robyn-fever-ray-first-aid-kit-among-1000-swedish-artists-calling-for-eurovision-to-ban-israel-3579906">呼吁今年禁止 Israel</a> ，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robyn">Robyn</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fever-ray">Fever Ray</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/first-aid-kit">First Aid Kit</a>等。超过<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/finnish-artists-sign-petition-calling-for-israel-to-be-banned-from-eurovision-3569080">1,400 名芬兰音乐界专业人士签署了一份请愿书，禁止该国参加这项比赛</a>。</p><p>以色列最终被允许参加比赛，并且由于政治中立条款，EBU 宣布他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eurovision-have-banned-palestinian-flags-and-symbols-3753455">保留移除巴勒斯坦旗帜和标志的权利</a>。他们后来继续<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/deleted-tiktok-reveals-moment-bambie-thug-was-forced-to-remove-pro-palestinian-message-its-fucked-up-3755454">审查爱尔兰选手 Bambie Thug，因为她在服装上隐藏了“停火”和“巴勒斯坦自由”字样</a>。</p><p>此外，今年的争议也随之而来，组织者在比赛前几个小时<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-netherlands-eurovision-entry-joost-klein-kicked-out-of-competition-3755424">取消了荷兰选手乔斯特·克莱因(Joost Klein)的参赛资格</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3611422" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3611422" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3611422" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/becky-hill-press-1.jpg" alt="贝基·希尔" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/becky-hill-press-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/becky-hill-press-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/becky-hill-press-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/becky-hill-press-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/becky-hill-press-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/becky-hill-press-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3611422" class="wp-caption-text">贝基·希尔.图片来源：Drapes SD</figcaption></figure><p>在贝基·希尔的其他新闻中，她的第二张录音室专辑<a href="https://www.n